PureÌe 1/4 cup vinegar, 2 tablespoons horseradish, and garlic in a food processor. With motor running, gradually add oil in a slow, steady stream through the feed tube; process until well combined, then add heavy cream. Season dressing with salt, pepper, and more vinegar and horseradish, if desired. DO AHEAD: Can be made 3 days ahead. Store chilled in an airtight jar.
